title: Lil Baby Interview

description:
Today on the show we had rapper Lil Baby stop by where he spoke about fatherhood, youngthug as a mentor and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Brian Williams from MSNBC for his mathematical error. Moreover, after Dababy made headlines from assaulting a woman at his show we opened up the phone lines to hear what our listeners thought about it?
